Package netx.jnlp.event

This package contains the JNLP events.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ApplicationListener The listener that is notified when an application instance is terminated.
DownloadListener The listener that is notified of the state of resources being downloaded by a ResourceTracker.
 

Class Summary
ApplicationEvent This event is sent when an application is terminated.
DownloadEvent This event is sent during the launch of an application.
